**Javascript**

Javascript makes web page interactive eg buttons, alerts. information storage
Javascript is made up of statements, variables, operators, and functions
Javascript at end of HTML / CSS

If want to set up a password
(1) set up password page
(2) set up main page to be password protected
(3) when do <a href....> each page points to the other
(4) 
